description: The associated files are mass spec data from 4 separate mixed-bed ion exchange column separations of Arabidopsis thaliana Col-0 seedling native extract.  Two fractionations used extract from seedlings grown in light and two fractionations used extract from etiolated seedlings (grown in the dark).  All fractions were processed similarly for LC-MS/MS but one light-grown fractionation was analyzed on a different mass spectrometer than the other three sets of ion exchange fractions.
